{"tid":1328653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿易戰一年，生產加快遷出中國！日經：逾 50 家考慮轉移","createTime":"2019-07-18T03:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T07:37:44.000Z","uid":141151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b823700d3616a5e7049130f7625870e969c632d","tid":1328653,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:41:56.000Z","msg":"貿易戰一年，生產加快遷出中國！日經：逾 50 家考慮轉移<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2019/07/18/over-50-companies-move-out-cn/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2019%2F07%2F18%2Fover-50-companies-move-out-cn%2F&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=23920041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2019/07/18/over-50-companies-move-out-cn/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">日經新聞 18 日報導，美中貿易戰開打後（美中相互發動制裁關稅以來），已過一年時間，而企業正加快將生產據點遷出中國，根據日經新聞向企業進行採訪以及根據各地媒體的報導顯示，因憂心美中貿易戰長期化，因此包含蘋果（Apple）、任天堂（Nintendo）、華碩等企業，超過 50 家全球主要企業考慮生產轉移，將部分產能遷出中國。</span><br />\n<br />\n據零件廠等多位關係人士指出，蘋果無線耳機「AirPods」代工廠中國歌爾聲學將在數週內於越南測試性生產最新機種，之後開始量產，此將是「AirPods」首度在中國以外的地方生產。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，外資企業佔中國整體進出口比重達四成，一旦生產轉移全面展開，恐將衝擊中國經濟。根據中國國家統計局指出，2017 年外資企業的物品進出口額約 1.8 兆美元，佔中國整體比重超過四成。截至 2017 年底，外資以及香港、台灣系企業在中國市區的雇用人數合計約 2,600 萬人，佔整體比重約 15%。"},{"pid":"082dd8f4669a95a39908e66a7d0aa31c29527f5b","tid":1328653,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:43:11.000Z","msg":"福布斯都咁講<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/kenrapoza/2019/07/16/europe-joins-us-companies-moving-out-of-china/#768cdda015bf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fkenrapoza%2F2019%2F07%2F16%2Feurope-joins-us-companies-moving-out-of-china%2F%23768cdda015bf&d=bTkwEGnHH2OXdpYsGZaakphbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=c788ce7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/kenrapoza/2019/07/16/europe-joins-us-companies-moving-out-of-china/#768cdda015bf</a>"},{"pid":"7ea6326773cf210c1c7754c5ec453615d125a287","tid":1328653,"uid":54181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:44:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd47092c38ea55326561a50d1594f9f088e3fd95","tid":1328653,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1703be62ed46dda7d8fde14ab9914f6969b7bb6","tid":1328653,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"就算之後美帝撤關稅<br />\nD廠都未必再搬反大陸<br />\n亦都因為d公司已經成功響中國以外設廠<br />\n將來都唔會響中國起新廠而係其他地方<br />\n今鋪就算打唔冧中國<br />\n亦都好有效限制中國發展速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac586edb4717eba981b40fe2583dc750e18f502","tid":1328653,"uid":41891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:54:15.000Z","msg":"心動不如行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再慢慢考慮"},{"pid":"ff09680ecd39c741452a9846a8b49cc43878e8ff","tid":1328653,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1703be62ed46dda7d8fde14ab9914f6969b7bb6","tid":1328653,"uid":134683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"就算之後美帝撤關稅<br />\nD廠都未必再搬反大陸<br />\n亦都因為d公司已經成功響中國以外設廠<br />\n將來都唔會響中國起新廠而係其他地方<br />\n今鋪就算打唔冧中國<br />\n亦都好有效限制中國發展速度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T04:58:30.000Z","msg":"搬返入去又一大舊錢, 不了."},{"pid":"b49e5b136f40248e1bf44426e2714bebf68f050f","tid":1328653,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac586edb4717eba981b40fe2583dc750e18f502","tid":1328653,"uid":41891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T03:54:15.000Z","msg":"心動不如行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再慢慢考慮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T05:00:12.000Z","msg":"有d公司好撚懶既<br />\n唔到死果刻都唔肯搬<br />\n<br />\n因為支那配套齊<br />\n去其他地方要source過晒所有物料,仲要未必齊"},{"pid":"daf530053